data.description: Welcome to your luxurious oasis. This exquisite 6-bedroom, 4-baths property offers the ultimate escape, with an abundance of features that will transform your everyday life into an endless treat.  As you step inside, you are greeted by a stunning 2-story foyer, setting the stage for the grandeur that lies within. The focal point of the home is the captivating 2-story great room, bathed in natural light, and featuring a wall of windows that frame the beauty of your surroundings. This is where memories will be made, laughter will echo, and relaxation will come effortlessly.  The heart of the home, your kitchen, is a chef's delight. Boasting a spacious island and gleaming stainless steel appliances, including a double oven, it's a culinary dream come true. Whether you're whipping up a gourmet meal or simply enjoying a leisurely breakfast, this space is designed to inspire.  Movie nights take on a whole new dimension in your basement's movie room – the perfect retreat for cinematic adventures with family and friends. When you're not in the theater, the beautiful 2nd-story deck offers a private spot to unwind and take in the stunning views or the silence of the night. Outside, the even backyard offers a serene escape from the everyday hustle and bustle. It's a canvas for your outdoor dreams – from BBQs to stargazing nights, the possibilities are endless.  This property is more than a home; it's a treat, a retreat, a sanctuary where every day feels like a getaway. Don't miss the chance to make it yours. Contact us today and let your dreams come true in this spectacular residence.
